      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved level must meet or exceed required level for model risk level 3.",
      "rationale": "Linear elastic continuum FEA model adopted for titanium alloy components. Material nonlinearity excluded based on load regime remaining within elastic range per F1717 protocol. Frictional contact at screw-rod interface modeled with Coulomb friction coefficient calibrated to literature values."
