      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved level must meet or exceed required level for model risk level 3.",
      "rationale": "N=11 physical constructs assembled from production-intent components by trained technicians following ASTM F1717 assembly procedures. Lot traceability documented. Sample size sufficient for statistical comparison at the required credibility level."
