      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved level must meet or exceed required level for model risk level 3.",
      "rationale": "Testing performed under a single load condition (axial compression-bending at 5° offset) per ASTM F1717. Additional load cases such as torsion or lateral bending were not included in this validation activity, limiting coverage of the full loading envelope relevant to in vivo use. This factor is below the required level and constitutes an identified gap."
