      "rationale": "Construct stiffness (N/mm) compared between FEA predictions and experimental measurements using Bland-Altman analysis and 95% prediction intervals. FEA ensemble mean within 8% of experimental mean; all FEA predictions fall within experimental 95% PI."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
